  "description": {
    "en-US": "Travel phrases for South Korea with audio, built for subway transfers, T-money reloads, Kakao T rides, hotel check-ins, cafes, and restaurant ordering.",
    "zh-CN": "韩国旅行短语卡，围绕地铁换乘、T-money 充值、Kakao T 打车、酒店入住、咖啡店和餐厅点单等高频场景整理。"
  },
  "intro": {
    "en-US": "Built for South Korea trips where you move between airport rail, subway exits, convenience stores, cafes, and barbecue places. These cards help when you need quick Korean for T-money, station exits, self-order kiosks, or handing a driver an address from Naver Map.",
    "zh-CN": "这套韩国短语优先覆盖机场铁路、地铁出入口、便利店、咖啡店和烤肉店这些常见场景。遇到要问 T-money、确认几号出口、处理自助点餐机，或给司机看 Naver Map 地址时，短语卡会特别省事。"
  },
  "teaser": {
    "en-US": "Built for Seoul-style travel with T-money, Kakao T, station exits, convenience stores, and cafe orders.",
    "zh-CN": "适合首尔式旅行里的 T-money、Kakao T、地铁出口、便利店和咖啡点单沟通。"
  },
  "travelTips": {
    "en-US": [
      "Keep transport phrases ready for subway line changes, station exit numbers, and T-money top-ups before you leave the airport.",
      "For taxis and late-night rides, it helps to show a Korean address from Naver Map or Kakao T together with the phrase card.",
      "Cafes, barbecue places, and self-order kiosks are easier when you can point to a short Korean request instead of typing a translation."
    ],
    "zh-CN": [
      "从机场进城前，最好先备好地铁换线、几号出口和 T-money 充值相关短语。",
      "打车尤其是深夜打车时，把 Naver Map 或 Kakao T 上的韩文地址和短语卡一起给司机看会更顺。",
      "在咖啡店、烤肉店或自助点餐机前，直接指着简短韩语短语，比现场打翻译快很多。"
    ]
  },
  "highlights": {
    "en-US": [
      "T-money and Kakao T",
      "Subway exits, cafes, and BBQ",
      "Hotels, kiosks, and convenience stores"
    ],
    "zh-CN": [
      "T-money 与 Kakao T",
      "地铁出口、咖啡店与烤肉店",
      "酒店、自助机与便利店"
    ]
  },
  "featured": true,
